{"abstract": "BET Networks, the television network owned by Viacom, is the latest media company to create a festival \u2014 pairing an array of marquee events with big sponsors.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/28/business/media/on-the-concert-stage-bet-festival-offers-a-broad-brand-experience.html", "snippet": "BET Networks, the television network owned by Viacom, is the latest media company to create a festival \u2014 pairing an array of marquee events with big sponsors.", "lead_paragraph": "MAGAZINES like The New Yorker and Essence, along with a growing number of media companies, have turned to literary and music festivals to extend the reach of their brands and draw consumers with live experiences and marquee names. But they have also found that festivals are a way for their sponsors to cut through the clutter of everyday advertising and touch consumers. ", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "7", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/28/business/Adco2/Adco2-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 849, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2013/06/28/business/Adco2/Adco2-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 849}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/28/business/Adco2/Adco2-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 724, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/28/business/Adco2/Adco2-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 1447, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/06/28/business/Adco2/Adco2-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumb